      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis maintains its composure with a factory-spec limited-slip differential and optimized weight distribution. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. While showing minor signs of road use consistent with its enthusiast history, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain sharp. A driver-focused machine with the iconic metallic rasp of the dual-exhaust system and a 8,000 RPM redline, it offers a pure analog driving experience.",
